  └─ { supportVision: true/false }
       │
       ▼
model-service.ts: fetchUserModels()
  ├─ httpGet() → RawModelInfo[]
  ├─ normalize: supportVision → supportsMultimodal  ← 新增映射（仅此处）
  ├─ L1 内存缓存 (supportsMultimodal 已填充)
  ├─ 磁盘缓存 (supportsMultimodal 已落盘)
  └─ getPlatformChannel() → ChannelModel { supportsMultimodal } ✓ 已生效
       │
       ▼
platform-models/atoms → PlatformModelInfo[] (supportsMultimodal 有效)
       │
       ▼
PlatformModelsSection.tsx
  └─ PlatformModelRow
       ├─ 模型名称
